<br>
Yes, Battlesongs reduces the variance of spell damage.  If you specced high in Battlesongs, you won't see much effect (if any) but if you specced lower than normal, then load up on +Battlesong items the damage variance will flatten out.  <br>
<br>
Remember, using +Battlesong items to raise your Battlesong skill will not grant you the higher level songs.  It also will not effect resists to your songs.<br>
<br>
